#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Vampiric Stuff"
msgstr "吸血鬼物品"

#. ~ Description for Vampiric Stuff
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"\n"
"<color_red>Adds night creatures, new items, monsters and locations.</color>\n"
"<color_light_red>More on interactions with npcs and quests, providing a subtle RPG playstyle.\n"
"\n"
"<color_light_cyan>Note that this mod is currently in <color_light_green>stable</color> state. Bugs rarely appears, but if you encounter one or a recent CDDA update has caused an error, feel free to notify the author by creating an issue on its GitHub repository or sending a PM on Discord.</color>"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"<color_red>添加夜行生物、新物品、怪物和地點。</color>\n"
"<color_light_red>增強與NPC的互動和任務，提供細膩的RPG玩法。</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color_light_cyan>請注意，此模組目前處於<color_light_green>穩定</color>狀態。雖然很少出現錯誤，但如果您遇到任何問題，或最近的CDDA更新導致了錯誤，請隨時通過在GitHub倉庫創建問題或在Discord上發送私信通知作者。</color>"

#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid "Red Velvets - The Dark Fashion"
msgid_plural "Red Velvets - The Dark Fashions"
msgstr[0] "紅絲絨 - 暗黑時尚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Red Velvets - The Dark Fashion'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"A somewhat horrifying book of sophisticated blood clothing. Much of its "
"content are trash and filled with monochrome images."
msgstr "一本略帶恐怖氣息的精緻血衣圖鑑。書中大部分內容都是垃圾，充斥著單色圖片。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid "Glorious Gunnery"
msgid_plural "Glorious Gunnerys"
msgstr[0] "榮耀槍械"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Glorious Gunnery'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"A rather advanced gun listing with photos and descriptions. It has "
"everything in it, including a complex, but understandable session of "
"creation."
msgstr "一本相當高級的槍械圖鑑，配有照片和描述。內容包羅萬象，包括一個複雜但易於理解的製作流程講解。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid "The Vampiric Infusion"
msgid_plural "The Vampiric Infusions"
msgstr[0] "吸血鬼灌注術"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'The Vampiric Infusion'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"This book holds almost all the basics of blood infusion that improves "
"efficiency and lethality of certain items. The half of this book is written "
"in a different language, leaving it unreadable... Unless you are able to get"
" translations."
msgstr "這本書涵蓋了幾乎所有血液灌注的基礎知識，能提升特定物品的效能與殺傷力。其中一半內容用另一種語言書寫，令人無法讀懂……除非你能找到翻譯。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid "Gravedigger's page note"
msgid_plural "Gravedigger's page notes"
msgstr[0] "掘墓人的頁邊筆記"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Gravedigger's page note"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"A piece of paper with a hand drawn picture of a pale man holding a heavily "
"blood stained sword impaled amongst the pile of corpses, which is gruesome "
"to look at. Under the photo is a note, which is blurry and unreadable."
msgstr "一張紙上畫著手繪圖：一個蒼白男子手持血跡斑斑的長劍，刺穿屍堆，景象令人毛骨悚然。圖下方有一行模糊難辨的筆記。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Gravedigger's page note"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"A piece of paper with a hand drawn picture of a beautiful lady on top of a "
"cliff, holding her bow gracefully. Written under it is Invynel, with an "
"inspiring short folklore about her."
msgstr "一張紙上畫著手繪圖：一位美麗的女士優雅持弓，立於懸崖之巔。下方寫著“英薇奈爾”，並附有一段關於她的勵志短篇傳說。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Gravedigger's page note"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"A simple hand drawn picture of an odd dagger, with engravings of ancient "
"language of some sort."
msgstr "一幅簡單的手繪圖，描繪了一把古怪的匕首，上面刻有某種古老語言的銘文。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Gravedigger's page note"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"Crushed human corpses and a huge, bloody hammer, this is what you only see "
"on this drawn picture."
msgstr "被碾碎的人類屍體與一柄巨大的血染戰錘——這便是這幅畫作中僅能看到的景象。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Gravedigger's page note"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"A bloody fight between medieval humans and a vampire with odd, brawling "
"knuckles at a castle corridor background, much like an invasion. This hand "
"drawn picture has shown nothing else."
msgstr "一幅以城堡走廊為背景的手繪圖，描繪了中世紀人類與一名佩戴古怪搏擊拳套的吸血鬼之間的血腥戰鬥，宛如一場入侵。畫中再無其他內容。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Gravedigger's page note"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_books.json
msgid ""
"A succulent fanged sword, oddly deformed with its rusty dull blade. Its "
"heavily burnt bottom page made it vaguely understandable of what it is."
msgstr "一把多汁的獠牙劍，因鏽蝕鈍化的劍身而畸形扭曲。其底部頁面嚴重燒焦，僅能勉強辨認出它是什麼。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_note.json
msgid "apprentice's note"
msgid_plural "apprentice's notes"
msgstr[0] "學徒筆記"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "apprentice's note"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_note.json
msgid "A torn-up paper. Something's written on it."
msgstr "一張撕碎的紙片。上面寫著一些字跡。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_scrolls.json
msgid "Spell Scroll"
msgid_plural "Spell Scrolls"
msgstr[0] "法術卷軸"

#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_scrolls.json
msgid "scroll of ancient vampiric wisdom"
msgid_plural "scroll of ancient vampiric wisdoms"
msgstr[0] "古老吸血鬼智慧卷軸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'scroll of ancient vampiric wisdom'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Books\v_scrolls.json
msgid ""
"Written in an unreadable language. With just a glimpse, you learn how to "
"cast all vampiric spells!"
msgstr "以無法讀懂的文字書寫。僅需一瞥，你便學會了如何施展所有吸血鬼法術！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_FANCIES.json
msgid "bloodrune necklace"
msgid_plural "bloodrune necklaces"
msgstr[0] "血符石項鍊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloodrune necklace'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_FANCIES.json
msgid ""
"An odd necklace with rescaled beautiful bloodrune stone to fit and attach to"
" the center. The thinned layer caused the core to pulsate faster."
msgstr "一條古怪的項鍊，中心鑲嵌著按比例縮放的精美血符石。變薄的石層使得核心搏動得更快。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_FANCIES.json
msgid "bloodrune talisman"
msgid_plural "bloodrune talismans"
msgstr[0] "血符石護符"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloodrune talisman'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_FANCIES.json
msgid ""
"An odd necklace with a beautifully etched bloodrune stone in eagle's talon "
"shape. If you prick your fingertip in its sharp point, you feel your blood "
"rushing towards it."
msgstr "一條古怪的項鍊，墜著一枚雕刻精美的鷹爪形血符石。若將指尖刺入其尖銳頂端，你會感到血液正向它奔湧而去。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_FANCIES.json
msgid "bloodrune ring"
msgid_plural "bloodrune rings"
msgstr[0] "血符石戒指"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloodrune ring'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_FANCIES.json
msgid ""
"A shimmering bloodrune ring with a tiny etched symbol under it. A proof of "
"loyalty to the commando."
msgstr "一枚閃爍的血符文戒指，下方刻有微小符號。這是對突擊隊忠誠的證明。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid "blood sheet ankle sheath"
msgid_plural "blood sheet ankle sheaths"
msgstr[0] "血片腳踝鞘"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'blood sheet ankle sheath'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'blood sheet wrist sheath'}.
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid "You have sheath your %s"
msgstr "你已將%s收入鞘中"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'blood sheet ankle sheath'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'blood sheet wrist sheath'}.
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid "Sheath knife"
msgstr "收鞘刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood sheet ankle sheath'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid ""
"A blood red, improvised ankle sheath, its material makes it tough and easier"
" to wear.  Activate to sheathe/draw a knife."
msgstr "一個血紅色的臨時腳踝鞘，其材質使其堅韌且易於佩戴。激活以收鞘/拔出刀具。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid "blood sheet wrist sheath"
msgid_plural "blood sheet wrist sheaths"
msgstr[0] "血片手腕鞘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood sheet wrist sheath'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid ""
"A blood red wrist sheath. Small weapons are quickly drawn under your hands, "
"just like what assassins do, but untrained people can hurt themselves.  "
"Activate to fast sheath/draw a knife."
msgstr "一個血紅色的手腕鞘。小型武器能迅速從你手中抽出，如同刺客所為，但未經訓練者可能傷及自身。激活以快速收鞘/拔出刀具。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid "bloodpack"
msgid_plural "bloodpacks"
msgstr[0] "血包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloodpack'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid ""
"Handcrafted backpack made of tough blood compact sheets customized to occupy"
" large amount of storage at a cost of encumbrance."
msgstr "手工製作的揹包，由堅韌的血凝片定製而成，以增加負重為代價換取大量存儲空間。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid "large bloodpack"
msgid_plural "large bloodpacks"
msgstr[0] "大型血包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bloodpack'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\v_bloodgear.json
msgid ""
"Improved bloodpack with additional pocket arrangements around it for even "
"larger storage occupation. Encumbrance and weight has increased, tho."
msgstr "改進型血包，周圍增加了額外口袋佈局以提供更大的存儲空間，但負重和重量也隨之提升。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid "blood infused survivor hood"
msgid_plural "blood infused survivor hoods"
msgstr[0] "血注倖存者兜帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood infused survivor hood'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid ""
"An improved hood combined with leather, kevlar and blood compact sheet. The "
"protection it used to provide has increased."
msgstr "一款改進的兜帽，結合了皮革、凱夫拉和血凝片。其提供的防護能力已得到增強。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid "blood infused survivor cargo pants"
msgid_plural "blood infused survivor cargo pantss"
msgstr[0] "血注倖存者工裝褲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood infused survivor cargo pants'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid ""
"A pair of pants consisting of leather, kevlar and blood compact sheet, "
"pouches and pockets are covered with excess materials for better protection."
" It is comfortable and warm."
msgstr "一條由皮革、凱夫拉和血凝片製成的褲子，口袋和包袋覆蓋了額外材料以提供更好防護。它舒適且保暖。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid "blood infused survivor duster"
msgid_plural "blood infused survivor dusters"
msgstr[0] "血注倖存者風衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood infused survivor duster'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid ""
"Customize kevlar duster with sleeves improved with blood compact sheets for "
"increased protection. The storage remains high."
msgstr "定製的凱夫拉風衣，袖子採用血凝片改進以增強防護。存儲容量保持較高水平。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid "pair of blood infused survivor gloves"
msgid_plural "pair of blood infused survivor glovess"
msgstr[0] "血注倖存者手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of blood infused survivor gloves'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid ""
"Customized pair of kevlar, leather and blood sheet compact gloves. It "
"provides protection in extreme situations."
msgstr "定製的凱夫拉、皮革和血凝片手套。它在極端情況下提供防護。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid "pair of blood infused survivor boots"
msgid_plural "pair of blood infused survivor bootss"
msgstr[0] "血注倖存者靴子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of blood infused survivor boots'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid ""
"Kevlar, leather and blood compact sheets arranged into the boots, granting "
"maximum damage protection against all odds."
msgstr "凱夫拉、皮革和血凝片組合製成的靴子，提供最大程度的傷害防護以應對一切險境。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid "blood infused survivor trenchcoat"
msgid_plural "blood infused survivor trenchcoats"
msgstr[0] "血浸倖存者風衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood infused survivor trenchcoat'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Infused\v_bloodinfusedset.json
msgid ""
"A trenchcoat built for both protection and storage using kevlar and blood "
"compact sheet. Comfortable to wear."
msgstr "一件採用凱夫拉和血凝板製成的風衣，兼顧防護與存儲功能，穿著舒適。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid "blood suit"
msgid_plural "blood suits"
msgstr[0] "血裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood suit'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight, blood red suit made completely of flexible blood compact "
"sheets and designed to be worn under your clothes. Protects vital "
"extremeties."
msgstr "一套輕便的血紅色套裝，完全由柔性血凝板製成，設計用於穿在衣物內層，保護關鍵肢體部位。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid "blood leather hood"
msgid_plural "blood leather hoods"
msgstr[0] "血革兜帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood leather hood'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid ""
"Hood made from compact blood and leather, this is tough and provides decent "
"protection from damage."
msgstr "由血凝板和皮革製成的兜帽，堅固耐用，提供良好的傷害防護。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid "blood leather duster"
msgid_plural "blood leather dusters"
msgstr[0] "血革防塵大衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood leather duster'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid ""
"Consists of blood compact sheets and leather. This fleshy duster provides "
"good storage and cotton lining for warmth."
msgstr "由血凝板和皮革構成。這件肉質防塵大衣提供良好的存儲空間，並配有棉質襯裡以保暖。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid "pair of blood leather gloves"
msgid_plural "pair of blood leather glovess"
msgstr[0] "血革手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of blood leather gloves'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid ""
"A combination of blood compact sheets and leather. This pair of velvet "
"gloves offer great protection against environment."
msgstr "血凝板與皮革的結合。這雙天鵝絨手套能有效抵禦環境傷害。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid "blood leather pants"
msgid_plural "blood leather pantss"
msgstr[0] "血革長褲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood leather pants'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid ""
"A pair of pants created from leather and blood compact sheets. Offers decent"
" protection."
msgstr "一條由皮革和血凝板製成的長褲，提供不錯的防護。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid "pair of blood leather boots"
msgid_plural "pair of blood leather bootss"
msgstr[0] "血革靴子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of blood leather boots'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Armor_Set\Normal\v_bloodset.json
msgid ""
"Pair of boots made from tough leather and blood compact sheets. It's a great"
" choice for rough journeys."
msgstr "由堅韌皮革和血凝板製成的靴子，是崎嶇旅程的理想選擇。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_currency.json
msgid "VelvetyToken"
msgid_plural "VelvetyTokens"
msgstr[0] "天鵝絨令牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'VelvetyToken'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_currency.json
msgid ""
"A well-made, seemingly handcrafted crimson coin produced merely of blood "
"from unknown creature. Its one side is adorned in astounding etched "
"decorations, and the other shows an image of a man, with undecipherable text"
" below it."
msgstr "一枚製作精良、看似手工打造的深紅色硬幣，僅由未知生物的血製成。一面飾有驚人的蝕刻紋飾，另一面顯示一個男子的圖像，下方有難以辨認的文字。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "Blood Compact"
msgstr "血凝板"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "ripped"
msgstr "撕裂"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "sliced"
msgstr "切片"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "scratched"
msgstr "刮痕"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "cut"
msgstr "割破"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "shredded"
msgstr "粉碎"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "tattered"
msgstr "破爛"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "Ethereal"
msgstr "縹緲"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_material_type.json
msgid "invincible"
msgstr "無敵"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo_types.json
msgid "blood"
msgid_plural "blood"
msgstr[0] "血"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood', 'str_pl': 'blood'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "Blood, possibly that of a human.  Disgusting!"
msgstr "血液，可能是人類的。真噁心！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "melted bloodrune stone"
msgid_plural "melted bloodrune stones"
msgstr[0] "熔化的血符石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'melted bloodrune stone'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid ""
"Finely crushed and extremely heated bloodrune stone. It merely generates a "
"faint glow and seems to maintain its power in its phase."
msgstr "精細研磨並經過極度加熱的血符石。它僅發出微弱的光芒，似乎在其相態中維持著力量。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "bloodrune stone"
msgid_plural "bloodrune stones"
msgstr[0] "血符石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloodrune stone'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid ""
"A pleasant ruby stone, possibly owned by a vampire. Its core mimics a "
"heartbeat with unreadable marks appearing again and again from its outside "
"layer. The strange power seems to be used with certain crafts."
msgstr "一塊悅目的紅寶石石，可能為吸血鬼所有。其核心模仿心跳，外層不斷浮現無法解讀的標記。這種奇異的力量似乎用於某些工藝。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "large bloodrune stone"
msgid_plural "large bloodrune stones"
msgstr[0] "大型血符石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large bloodrune stone'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid ""
"A large bloodrune stone, seemingly compressed by an unknown source. It "
"trembles by its own, eager to shatter from its shell."
msgstr "一塊大型血符石，似乎被未知來源壓縮。它自行顫動，渴望從外殼中碎裂。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "sticky blood"
msgid_plural "sticky bloods"
msgstr[0] "粘稠血液"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sticky blood'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid ""
"A sticky, rounded human blood, as literally. Its adhesiveness is compare to "
"the regular superglues."
msgstr "一團粘稠、圓潤的人類血液，名副其實。其粘性堪比常規強力膠。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "blood powder"
msgid_plural "blood powders"
msgstr[0] "血粉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood powder'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "A powdered human blood. Perfect vampire getaway snacks."
msgstr "粉末狀的人類血液。完美的吸血鬼便攜零食。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "blood extract"
msgid_plural "blood extracts"
msgstr[0] "血液提取物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood extract'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "A sticky sap after the process of extraction from the blood."
msgstr "從血液中提取後得到的粘稠汁液。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "blood compact sheet"
msgid_plural "blood compact sheets"
msgstr[0] "血液壓實片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood compact sheet'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid ""
"Well compressed leathery sheet. It is known as an aesthetics clothing "
"material, due to its unique reddish appearance. But from now, it was proven "
"superior to armorcraft."
msgstr "壓制良好的皮革狀薄片。因其獨特的紅色外觀，被視為美學服裝材料。但如今，它已被證明在護甲工藝中更為優越。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "blood pellet"
msgid_plural "blood pellets"
msgstr[0] "血丸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood pellet'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Misc\v_materials.json
msgid "A tiny blood pellet, sparkling like bits of fined rubies."
msgstr "微小的血丸，如精煉紅寶石碎片般閃爍。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_qualities.json
msgid "blood infusing"
msgstr "血液灌注"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_qualities.json
msgid "blood refining"
msgstr "血液精煉"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_qualities.json
msgid "blood compressing"
msgstr "血液壓縮"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_qualities.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_tools.json
msgid "blood chemistry"
msgid_plural "blood chemistrys"
msgstr[0] "血液化學"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_tools.json
msgid "blood infusing forge"
msgid_plural "blood infusing forges"
msgstr[0] "血液灌注熔爐"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood infusing forge'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_tools.json
msgid ""
"A primitive tool used in vampiric crafts. This is much like of a normal "
"forge, but it requires the correct materials to work with it. Uses normal "
"batteries whatsoever."
msgstr "一種用於吸血鬼工藝的原始工具。它很像普通熔爐，但需要正確的材料才能運作。使用普通電池。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_tools.json
msgid "blood extractor"
msgid_plural "blood extractors"
msgstr[0] "血液提取器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood extractor'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_tools.json
msgid ""
"A small, heating container used in extracting water components from blood, "
"turning it into a powder speckles. It uses common batteries."
msgstr "一種小型加熱容器，用於從血液中提取水分，將其轉化為粉末顆粒。使用普通電池。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_tools.json
msgid "blood compressor"
msgid_plural "blood compressors"
msgstr[0] "血液壓縮機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood compressor'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_tools.json
msgid ""
"A large, essential compressing tool to make blood compacts from vast amounts"
" of powders. The tiny tissue filaments of human cells will be reinforced "
"into a strong and tough, leathery sheets, which is then be tailored into "
"clothing. High battery consumption per use."
msgstr "一種大型的必備壓縮工具，用於將大量粉末製成血塊。人體細胞的微小組織纖維會被強化成堅韌的皮革狀薄片，然後裁剪成衣物。每次使用耗電量高。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood chemistry'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Tools\v_tools.json
msgid ""
"A simple blood chemistry set, much look like a copied version of human's. It"
" has the complete tools in making chemicals and adhesives for essential "
"projects."
msgstr "一套簡單的血液化學裝置，看起來很像人類版本的複製品。它包含製作化學品和粘合劑所需的完整工具，用於基本項目。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid "shaken blood"
msgid_plural "shaken bloods"
msgstr[0] "搖晃過的血液"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shaken blood'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Blood which has slightly thickened from intense shaking. Almost compatible "
"with vampiric guns if you're desperately need to feed them."
msgstr "經過劇烈搖晃後略微變稠的血液。如果你急需為吸血鬼槍械供能，它幾乎兼容。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid "pressurized blood"
msgid_plural "pressurized bloods"
msgstr[0] "加壓血液"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pressurized blood'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Cheap and renewable. This heavily compressed blood ammunition is used "
"specifically with certain vampiric guns."
msgstr "廉價且可再生。這種高度壓縮的血液彈藥專門用於某些吸血鬼槍械。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid "traversed blood"
msgid_plural "traversed bloods"
msgstr[0] "混合血液"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'traversed blood'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Cheap and easy to collect. A combination of pure and infected blood and much"
" more viscous than others."
msgstr "廉價且易於收集。純淨血液與感染血液的混合物，比其他類型更粘稠。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid "00 bloodshot"
msgid_plural "00 bloodshots"
msgstr[0] "00號血彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '00 bloodshot'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reloaded 00 bloodshot'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid ""
"Blood pellet-filled shot. Maximizes damage at very short range and will "
"cause spread pellets to explode into sharp bits, dealing additional damage "
"on impact. This is the only shotgun ammuminition developed and overused by "
"vampires due to its overall balancing power."
msgstr ""
"填充血丸的霰彈。在極近距離下最大化傷害，散佈的彈丸會爆炸成鋒利碎片，造成額外衝擊傷害。這是吸血鬼開發並過度使用的唯一霰彈彈藥，因其整體平衡性。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo.json
msgid "reloaded 00 bloodshot"
msgid_plural "reloaded 00 bloodshots"
msgstr[0] "重裝00號血彈"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ammo_types.json
msgid "bloodshot"
msgstr "血彈"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "blood sipper"
msgid_plural "blood sippers"
msgstr[0] "血液啜飲者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood sipper', 'str_pl': 'blood sippers'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A large, dual-handed, heavily serrated sword. The blade retracts into sharp "
"teeth-like formation everytime it is swung, while vice versa, it becomes "
"flat when not in use. The weight of this sword is problematic."
msgstr "一把大型、雙手持握、重度鋸齒的劍。每次揮動時，劍刃會收縮成尖銳的牙齒狀結構，反之，不使用時則變平。此劍的重量是個問題。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "blood sipper+"
msgid_plural "blood sippers+"
msgstr[0] "嗜血者+"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood sipper+', 'str_pl': 'blood sippers+'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A large, dual-handed, heavily serrated sword, textured in red hue. The blade"
" retracts into sharp teeth-like formation everytime it is swung, while vice "
"versa, it becomes flat when not in use. The weight of this sword is "
"problematic."
msgstr ""
"一把大型、雙手持握、帶有厚重鋸齒的劍，呈現紅色紋理。每次揮動時，劍刃會收縮成尖銳的牙齒狀結構，反之，不使用時則恢復平坦。此劍的重量是個問題。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "blood diver"
msgid_plural "blood divers"
msgstr[0] "血潛者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood diver', 'str_pl': 'blood divers'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A small, serrated dagger. Its handle is made for quick precise stabs, and "
"the lightweight of this weapon makes it versatile to use. The unique form of"
" its blade is great for skinning, but there's a better purpose other than "
"that."
msgstr "一把小型、帶鋸齒的匕首。其手柄設計用於快速精準的刺擊，武器的輕量化使其用途廣泛。獨特的刀刃形狀非常適合剝皮，但除此之外還有更好的用途。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "blood diver+"
msgid_plural "blood divers+"
msgstr[0] "血潛者+"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood diver+', 'str_pl': 'blood divers+'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A small, serrated dagger, textured in red hue. Its handle is designed for "
"quick precise stabs, and the weight of this weapon makes it versatile to "
"use. The unique form of its blade is great for skinning, but there's a "
"better purpose other than that."
msgstr ""
"一把小型、帶鋸齒的匕首，呈現紅色紋理。其手柄設計用於快速精準的刺擊，武器的重量使其用途廣泛。獨特的刀刃形狀非常適合剝皮，但除此之外還有更好的用途。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "pair of knuckle biters"
msgid_plural "pairs of Knuckle Biters"
msgstr[0] "指虎啃咬者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of knuckle biters', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. Knuckle Biters'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A pair of knuckles designed to imitate a jaw with heavily arranged metal "
"teeth. Every successful impacts will cause it to bite quickly to its prey."
msgstr "一副模仿顎部、帶有密集排列金屬牙齒的指虎。每次成功命中都會使其快速咬向獵物。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "pair of knuckle biters+"
msgid_plural "pairs of knuckle biters+"
msgstr[0] "指虎啃咬者+"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of knuckle biters+', 'str_pl': 'pairs of
#. knuckle biters+'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A pair of knuckles designed to imitate a jaw with heavily arranged metal "
"teeth, textured in red hue. Every successful impacts will cause it to bite "
"quickly to its prey."
msgstr "一副模仿顎部、帶有密集排列金屬牙齒的指虎，呈現紅色紋理。每次成功命中都會使其快速咬向獵物。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "hammerius"
msgid_plural "hammeriuses"
msgstr[0] "錘擊者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hammerius', 'str_pl': 'hammeriuses'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A huge, fearsome battle hammer. Its flattened surface has symmetric holes, "
"in which spikes are seen beneath it, and everytime you bash an opponent, it "
"retracts to puncture the prey's innards."
msgstr "一把巨大、駭人的戰錘。其平坦表面有對稱的孔洞，可見下方的尖刺，每次猛擊對手時，尖刺會收縮以刺穿獵物的內臟。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "hammerius+"
msgid_plural "hammeriuses+"
msgstr[0] "錘擊者+"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hammerius+', 'str_pl': 'hammeriuses+'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A huge, fearsome battle hammer, textured in red hue. Its flattened surface "
"has symmetric holes, in which spikes are seen, and everytime you bash an "
"opponent, it retracts to puncture the prey's inner flesh."
msgstr "一把巨大、駭人的戰錘，呈現紅色紋理。其平坦表面有對稱的孔洞，可見尖刺，每次猛擊對手時，尖刺會收縮以刺穿獵物的內部血肉。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "fanged falchion"
msgid_plural "fanged falchions"
msgstr[0] "獠牙彎刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fanged falchion'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A plain longsword with peculiar hilt and its forked tip imitates a pair of "
"fangs of some sort. Pretty easy to use and its weight is unique for such a "
"fearsome sword."
msgstr "一把樸素的長劍，帶有奇特的手柄，其分叉的尖端模仿某種獠牙。相當易於使用，其重量對於如此駭人的劍來說很獨特。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid "fanged falchion+"
msgid_plural "fanged falchions+"
msgstr[0] "獠牙彎刀+"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fanged falchion+', 'str_pl': 'fanged
#. falchions+'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\melee_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A plain longsword hued in crimson with peculiar hilt and its forked tip "
"imitates a pair of fangs of some sort. Pretty easy to use and its weight is "
"unique for such a fearsome sword."
msgstr "一把深紅色調的樸素長劍，帶有奇特的手柄，其分叉的尖端模仿某種獠牙。相當易於使用，其重量對於如此駭人的劍來說很獨特。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "Invynel's bow"
msgid_plural "Invynel's bows"
msgstr[0] "因維內爾之弓"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A heavy, steel bow. Its serrated, blade handle makes it available for melee,"
" but unwieldy. Well trained archers find this useful for long to mid range "
"combats greatly."
msgstr "一把沉重的鋼製弓。其帶鋸齒的刀刃手柄可用於近戰，但難以操控。訓練有素的弓箭手發現這在遠至中程戰鬥中非常有用。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "blood striker"
msgid_plural "blood strikers"
msgstr[0] "血擊者"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A modified and beautifully designed striker shotgun created by vampires. "
"Unlike human's, it has a bigger revolving wheel, which occupies additional "
"bullets and a 3-shot burst mode for barraging shots with its improved "
"accuracy."
msgstr ""
"一款由吸血鬼改造並精美設計的打擊者霰彈槍。與人類的版本不同，它擁有更大的旋轉彈輪，可容納額外彈藥，並具備三連發點射模式，配合其提升的精準度進行壓制射擊。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "burst"
msgstr "連發"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "blood slinger"
msgid_plural "blood slingers"
msgstr[0] "血彈槍"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight vampiric gun with special mounted blood-fed container. It uses"
" thickened blood as the primary ammunition, and shoots at high velocity, "
"regardless of its small size."
msgstr "一款輕量化的吸血鬼槍械，配有特殊安裝的血液供給容器。它使用濃縮血液作為主要彈藥，儘管體積小巧，卻能以高速射擊。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "blood stinger"
msgid_plural "blood stingers"
msgstr[0] "血刺槍"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A unique vampiric gun with specially designed barrel and a built-in blood-"
"feed container input method. It uses thickened blood as the primary "
"ammunition, and shoots at extremely high velocity, dealing damage nearly the"
" same to high caliber firearms."
msgstr ""
"一款獨特的吸血鬼槍械，擁有專門設計的槍管和內置的血液供給輸入方式。它使用濃縮血液作為主要彈藥，以極高的速度射擊，造成的傷害幾乎與大口徑火器相當。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "blood stream shooter"
msgid_plural "blood stream shooters"
msgstr[0] "血流噴射槍"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A heavy vampiric gun with very large, built-in blood-feed container input "
"method and a trio-rotational barrel chambers. It uses thickened blood as the"
" primary ammunition, and shoots at maximum firing rate without generating "
"disrupting sounds."
msgstr "一款重型吸血鬼槍械，配有非常龐大的內置血液供給輸入方式和三重旋轉槍膛。它使用濃縮血液作為主要彈藥，以最大射速射擊，且不會產生干擾性噪音。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "5 rd."
msgstr "5發"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\shot_method.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid "blood sprayer"
msgid_plural "blood sprayers"
msgstr[0] "血霧噴射器"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight vampiric gun with large, built-in blood-feed container input "
"method. It uses thickened blood as the primary ammunition, and shoots at "
"high firing rate without generating disrupting sounds."
msgstr "一款輕量化的吸血鬼槍械，配有大型內置血液供給輸入方式。它使用濃縮血液作為主要彈藥，以高射速射擊，且不會產生干擾性噪音。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon_mod.json
msgid "bloodstinger barrel"
msgid_plural "bloodstinger barrels"
msgstr[0] "血刺槍槍管"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon_mod.json
msgid ""
"Odd barrel extension specialized for blood stinger rifles. It has a vented "
"metal end point that pressurizes liquid before firing, increasing damage, "
"accuracy and aiming time."
msgstr "專為血刺槍步槍設計的奇特槍管延伸部件。它帶有一個通風金屬端點，可在射擊前對液體加壓，從而提高傷害、精準度和瞄準時間。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Items\Weapons\ranged_weapon_mod.json
msgid "barrel"
msgstr "槍管"

